{"tid":1482242,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[最後警示] 香港人要堅忍 香港人要堅忍 香港人要堅忍","createTime":"2019-08-18T04:37:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T04:51:32.000Z","uid":125938,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1c618fdfd89a3d3ddd536f4cf20157a4bf51300f","tid":1482242,"uid":125938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:37:43.000Z","msg":"班農了解中共 香港人要堅忍<br />\n<br />\n班農是極了解中共的美國元老，曾經是特朗普的首席策略顧問。而似乎全世界也清楚中共想做的事。中共在香港邊境聚集大量軍警，卻不開入香港，並非純粹要嚇阻香港的示威，而是在等待戲本安排。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">若果戰爭前線的武力上升，中共會混入人群，把幾個警察殺死，又或者是把載有警察的警車焚毀，活活燒死幾個。明日，更可能會衝擊解放軍軍營。這樣，中共就能按劇本，應警方的要求，把武警臨時編入警隊編制。製造大型鎮壓，以拿回中共的面子。</span><br />\n<br />\n最大問題，是會令美國無法就香港問題與中共談判。因為美國人民看到屠城般的鎮壓，必定會反對與中共和談，而是要求強硬制裁中共國。美國就失去介入香港的機會。香港則會演變出更大的武力衝突，<span style=\"color: red;\">建國完全治自的路途就更遙遠，制裁警察、補償義士的機會就更渺茫。</span><br />\n<br />\n所以，現在是堅忍之時。把勇武的力量潛藏，配合美國的攻勢。明日，希望各位戰士稍作整頓，靜待美國與中共國就香港事情的明確表態後，再作行動。這刻，美國也在靜待香港這週末，要確保中共的奸計未有成功，然後才能大舉揮軍。<br />\n<br />\n香港奮勇，是要取回本來屬於我們的自治權。血流了、犧牲了，現在終於獲得美國明確的支援，我們切勿在這刻又親自趕走這最強的盟友。現在堅忍，成就香港建國。<br />\n<br />\npray for hk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a80e756d5fcf0547753525db3cc3b05ff915cf","tid":1482242,"uid":125938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:37:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"08b2ee875f5fa834300e9c6866d38c97f4865530","tid":1482242,"uid":125938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:37:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5cefbc4346e33130ce3ba4615a719bb89522a055","tid":1482242,"uid":21552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:38:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"542c28e54d5255ed2e4461e8bf02a1be07f84a5d","tid":1482242,"uid":125938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:38:11.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"f4ba1e6bf810919af310e5496f9949bc5852fcd6","tid":1482242,"uid":125938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:38:23.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"15f96220af59a86e5d4297d990f449c719ce5a6b","tid":1482242,"uid":237528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:38:35.000Z","msg":"推 大家要堅忍<br />\n美國佬做緊野"},{"pid":"d86641a8ef7e59eeb25c369cfc12f29db7402629","tid":1482242,"uid":125938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:38:37.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"8a116e421f7ae008fd49675cf9c6e492ced30700","tid":1482242,"uid":69916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:38:41.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"927efa265c56292b345db98a0ed4b7ac5822da45","tid":1482242,"uid":139409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:38:46.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnf9O7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbnf9O7G.jpg&h=5ee9af01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=6ad5cf1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=6ad5cf1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"64ae431fc8eeb0421fe3f4826ceb915f4c7ec701","tid":1482242,"uid":125938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:38:48.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"d3d0236aff727e238d86f911f56d72b8aa929497","tid":1482242,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b682ea4a7b1c20be905cf5bbc6e8cb529e7c94","tid":1482242,"uid":125938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor